{"tid":1329802,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ONEPIECE 海賊王 第 949 話 中文情報","createTime":"2019-07-18T10:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T04:21:53.000Z","uid":130563,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ae644d4cbe33f46eed97c409617d6ce5eb95ab30","tid":1329802,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uxp2Lfx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxp2Lfx.jpg&h=96e758cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJUMP封面和卷頭彩頁都是海賊王。<br />\n一整話都是關於兔碗<br />\n路飛和小玉相見<br />\n<br />\n-彩頁是草帽一夥和大猩猩在泳池裡<br />\n-路飛和其他人正在打倒給賦者<br />\n-基德和基拉在圍觀戰鬥<br />\n-蝎子獄卒使用了疫災彈<br />\n-路飛試圖抓住感染的人結果被感染了<br />\n-路飛抓住了感染的人把他們扔到了遠處<br />\n-蝎子獄卒使用了化學子彈<br />\n-大象獄卒試圖用大象發射化學子彈200<br />\n-路飛把大象鼻子打了個結，然後大象自爆了<br />\n-路飛命令囚犯們攻擊蝎子獄卒<br />\n-然後路飛控制了監獄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.talkop.com/thread-116293-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.talkop.com%2Fthread-116293-1-1.html&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=e0b7d201\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.talkop.com/thread-116293-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"d8f4bc21597a045f45a561d75e42a2028ce674d3","tid":1329802,"uid":130563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mw5A5fS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMw5A5fS.jpg&h=853c8be2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c6c6ca7700c8134fbf03776d7ce9ccbd716d333","tid":1329802,"uid":128089,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"監獄班友邊度會夠路飛打 完全係搵戲嚟做"},{"pid":"2cf6f65bb477811cbe5abdc8d40714a5cc4f45ea","tid":1329802,"uid":402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"推this"},{"pid":"f23e2d5693afb41a57ffc3ae9b917b6b3c0dc0a0","tid":1329802,"uid":402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"#9心急到開錯係cc台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329708</a>"},{"pid":"0beddfe5f81a131ebcce1a6be21f048580952a38","tid":1329802,"uid":84247,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"feel到今話都好有政治色彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e4958faa6029ac7280ec347c062c6b470d0553","tid":1329802,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c6c6ca7700c8134fbf03776d7ce9ccbd716d333","tid":1329802,"uid":128089,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"監獄班友邊度會夠路飛打 完全係搵戲嚟做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7e8df178db6ad83f8bc5c06d299aa0a1684fb7","tid":1329802,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"明哥走甩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c128880f091d721b7e9567baf94210f00c2cba72","tid":1329802,"uid":115347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"化學彈是咪催淚彈"},{"pid":"a6e5c4eaa1091c50dd29152caaa041655c0f819b","tid":1329802,"uid":130563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"鼠繪詳細情報  <br />\n<br />\n第949話標題 殭屍<br />\n<br />\n看守們為了阻止路飛一行人開始發射由病毒製成的疫災彈。<br />\n他們的目標並不是路飛等人，而是無差別的向犯人們射擊。<br />\n被疫災彈打中會得一種傳染病，症狀為全身像燒傷一樣痛苦，直至死亡。<br />\n這個武器是由奎因製作出來的，名為「殭屍」。<br />\n<br />\n看守們命令那些中彈的犯人向路飛等人靠近，把他們當作生化武器。<br />\n犯人們十分痛苦地控訴道：如果沒有你們這些外人出現，我們不會變成這樣，就憑你們是無法戰勝凱多的，你們滾出去！<br />\n路飛聽後主動碰觸了這些感染的犯人們，並對他們大聲喊道：這種東西，根本無效！<br />\n<br />\n他繼續說道：我答應過小玉，要拯救這個國家，要讓大家都能吃飽飯，我們是來戰勝凱多！沒有理由被夥伴們阻止，你們決定吧，是跟著凱多還是我們！<br />\n犯人們都被路飛的這番話感動了。<br />\n<br />\n而巴巴努基正眼看不妙，打算趁機將大量的疫災彈投擲過去。<br />\n但是被路飛立即阻止了，因為路飛說他看到了危險的未來。<br />\n然後路飛轉身對犯人們說：剩下的就看你們的了！<br />\n距離決戰還有8天&mdash;&mdash;在沒被敵人大本營發現的情況下，壓制了免碗。"},{"pid":"cf67ca63d32540dd925d925cf750ef4d76b96374","tid":1329802,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"睇黎凱多係由大媽同路飛聯手打贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e4d6f2a19c1217d78dffcae3e78caade373a3d","tid":1329802,"uid":35978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，玩咁耐都仲有8天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e03ecf119f1bf1849d2bd990870fa3c5945cb23","tid":1329802,"uid":36676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f5e4d6f2a19c1217d78dffcae3e78caade373a3d","tid":1329802,"uid":35978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，玩咁耐都仲有8天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:06:50.000Z","msg":"8天=一年半"},{"pid":"f76e944c7c6afbdd6c8ce9d93b72e3bad8f32b8e","tid":1329802,"uid":247998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:33:32.000Z","msg":"竟然無下週休刊"},{"pid":"9510be5dc7a1fd4d08324de88ce2d41e6c3d4eb8","tid":1329802,"uid":55620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e03ecf119f1bf1849d2bd990870fa3c5945cb23","tid":1329802,"uid":36676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f5e4d6f2a19c1217d78dffcae3e78caade373a3d","tid":1329802,"uid":35978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，玩咁耐都仲有8天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:06:50.000Z","msg":"8天=一年半"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"明哥幾粒鐘都打左2-3年<br />\n8日邊可能咁短"},{"pid":"67e6c083e9df20527e4bb825e391d624b61e0315","tid":1329802,"uid":83578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:17:51.000Z","msg":"基德 食花生<br />\n佢會咁冷靜gar 咩？<img s